# Copy to deploy/.env and fill in.
#
# ── For the Stock Claude Hetzner box (Tailscale-private — the chosen path) ──
#    Used by deploy/deploy-tailscale.sh. See deploy/HETZNER_STOCKBOX.md.
WC_TS_PORT=8443          # tailscale-serve HTTPS port (must differ from stock's 443/8765)
WC_APP_PORT=8000         # local port the web app binds (must differ from 8765)
SERVICE_USER=root        # systemd service user on the box
# LIVE_API_KEY=          # optional private TheSportsDB key (public "3" works without one)

# ── For a fresh PUBLIC box with a domain (alternative — deploy/deploy.sh + Caddy) ──

# The domain you've pointed at the VPS (an A record -> the server's public IP).
WC_DOMAIN=wc.example.com

# Basic-auth gate for the public site.
WC_BASIC_USER=jack
WC_BASIC_PASSWORD=change-me-to-something-long

# Linux user the services run as. Defaults to the sudo-invoking user, else "wc".
# SERVICE_USER=wc

# Optional: a private TheSportsDB API key (the public free key "3" works without one).
# LIVE_API_KEY=
